@PersonalExpense.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5096

### Authentication - Register
POST {{PersonalExpense.API_HostAddress}}/api/account/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test12345!"
}

### Authentication - Login
# @name login
POST {{PersonalExpense.API_HostAddress}}/api/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test12345!"
}

### Get Token from login response
@token = {{login.response.body.$.token}}

### Accounts - Get All
GET {{PersonalExpense.API_HostAddress}}/api/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Accounts - Create Cash Account
POST {{PersonalExpense.API_HostAddress}}/api/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cash",
  "type": 1,
  "balance": 5000,
  "description": "Cash in hand"
}

### Accounts - Create Bank Account
POST {{PersonalExpense.API_HostAddress}}/api/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bank Card",
  "type": 2,
  "balance": 15000,
  "description": "Main bank account"
}

### Accounts - Create E-Wallet Account
POST {{PersonalExpense.API_HostAddress}}/api/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "E-Wallet",
  "type": 5,
  "balance": 1000,
  "description": "Mobile payment wallet"
}

### ============================================================================
### 多账户转账功能 - 成对流水转账（推荐）
### ============================================================================

### Transfer - Create Pair Transfer (Recommended)
# 功能说明：
# - 在两个账户之间进行转账
# - 生成成对流水：一条支出记录 + 一条收入记录
# - 两条记录通过 RelatedTransactionId 互相关联
# - 保证原子性：如果任意一步失败，全部回滚
#
# 请求参数说明：
# - fromAccountId: 转出账户ID
# - toAccountId: 转入账户ID  
# - amount: 转账金额（必须大于0）
# - transactionDate: 交易日期
# - description: 描述（可选）
#
# 返回结果：
# - outgoingTransaction: 转出交易记录（Type=Expense）
# - incomingTransaction: 转入交易记录（Type=Income）
# - 两条记录的 RelatedTransactionId 互相指向对方
POST {{PersonalExpense.API_HostAddress}}/api/transactions/transfer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 1000,
  "transactionDate": "2026-04-19T10:00:00Z",
  "description": "Transfer from Bank to Cash",
  "fromAccountId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "toAccountId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002"
}

### ============================================================================
### 余额变动查询
### ============================================================================

### Account Balance History - Get by Account
# 功能说明：
# - 按账户查看余额变动历史
# - 计算每笔交易后的账户余额
# - 统计总收入、总支出、净变化
#
# 请求参数说明：
# - accountId: 账户ID（路径参数）
# - startDate: 开始日期（可选，查询参数）
# - endDate: 结束日期（可选，查询参数）
#
# 返回结果说明：
# - accountId, accountName, accountType: 账户基本信息
# - startingBalance: 查询时间范围的起始余额
# - endingBalance: 查询时间范围的结束余额
# - totalIncome: 总收入
# - totalExpense: 总支出
# - netChange: 净变化（= totalIncome - totalExpense）
# - balanceHistory: 余额变动明细列表
#   - transactionDate: 交易日期
#   - description: 交易描述
#   - transactionType: 交易类型（Income/Expense/Transfer）
#   - amount: 交易金额
#   - balanceAfterTransaction: 该笔交易后的余额
#   - relatedTransactionId: 关联交易ID（成对转账时存在）
GET {{PersonalExpense.API_HostAddress}}/api/transactions/account/{{accountId}}/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Account Balance History - With Date Range
GET {{PersonalExpense.API_HostAddress}}/api/transactions/account/{{accountId}}/history?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### 对账功能 - 异常差额检测
### ============================================================================

### Reconciliation - Single Account
# 功能说明：
# - 对指定账户进行对账
# - 验证账户实际余额与交易记录计算的余额是否一致
# - 检测成对转账是否完整、金额是否匹配
#
# 检测项：
# 1. BalanceMismatch: 账户余额与交易历史计算结果不匹配
# 2. OrphanTransfer: 存在孤立的转账记录（关联交易缺失）
# 3. AmountMismatch: 成对转账金额不匹配
#
# 返回结果说明：
# - isBalanced: 是否平衡（无异常）
# - expectedBalance: 根据交易记录计算的预期余额
# - actualBalance: 账户实际余额
# - discrepancy: 差额（= expectedBalance - actualBalance）
# - discrepancies: 异常明细列表
GET {{PersonalExpense.API_HostAddress}}/api/reconciliation/account/{{accountId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reconciliation - All Accounts
# 功能说明：
# - 对用户所有账户进行对账
# - 返回每个账户的对账结果
# - 可用于批量检查所有账户状态
GET {{PersonalExpense.API_HostAddress}}/api/reconciliation/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reconciliation - Transfer Discrepancies
# 功能说明：
# - 专门检测转账相关的异常
# - 包括：
#   - MissingRelated: 缺少关联交易
#   - UnpairedTransfer: 未成对的传统转账
#
# 使用场景：
# - 排查转账操作失败导致的余额不一致
# - 检查系统迁移后的数据完整性
# - 定期审计转账记录的完整性
GET {{PersonalExpense.API_HostAddress}}/api/reconciliation/transfer-discrepancies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

